	<h1 class="scrollTitle">Content Management Systems</h1>
	
	<p>I created <b>Pixels</b> - a content management system and it has abilities to serve different types of websites. You could create and update your website without any knowledge of programming languages. The website types currently supported are:</p>
	
	<ul>
		<li>Basic website</li>
		<li>Basic plus News</li>
		<li>E-Commerce website</li>
		<li>E-Commerce plus News</li>
		<li>E-Hotel website</li>
		<li>E-Hotel plus News</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Front-end</h2>

	<p class="pageGalleryImg" style="float: none; margin: 0 auto;">
