	<h2 class="clear">Description of the modules</h2>

	<p><b>Basic website</b></p>

	<p>The basic website module could be corporate website, a small business website or personal website. Key features:<p>
	
	<ul>
		<li>Unlimited number of webpages</li>
		<li>Unlimited number of images</li>
		<li>Mobile friendly</li>
		<li>Drop-down header menu</li>
		<li>Footer menu</li>
		<li>Landing pages generator</li>
		<li>Files manager, files organizer into folders, drag and drop files directly from your browser into server's folders, drag and drop files from one folder into another</li>
		<li>Image sets uploader, two types of images sets, slider and gallery, drag dnd drop images directly from your browser. Drag and drop images to reorder.</li>
		<li>User account manager</li>
		<li>Website settings, logo, slogan, social network links</li>
		<li>Contract form and inbox with new emails notifications</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p class="pageGalleryImg">
		<a href="../../images/basicPixelsScreen.jpg">
			<img src="../../images/basicPixelsScreen.jpg" class="fullWidth">
			<span class="imgCaption">CMS, Main Pages</span>
		</a>
	</p>
	
	<p class="pageGalleryImg">
		<a href="../../images/pixelsManager1.jpg">
			<img src="../../images/pixelsManager1.jpg" class="fullWidth">
			<span class="imgCaption">CMS, drag and drop files directly from your browser into server's folders</span>
		</a>
	</p>
	
	<h2 class="clear">E-Commerce module</h2>
	
	<p>This module turns the website into a full featured web shop.</p>
	
	<ul>
		<li>Shopping cart</li>
		<li>Checkout pop-up</li>
		<li>Unlimited number of categories and subcategories ordered into a drop-down menu</li>
		<li>Unlimited number of products</li>
		<li>Back end new orders notifications</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p class="pageGalleryImg">
		<a href="../../images/shopCartScreen.jpg">
			<img src="../../images/shopCartScreen.jpg" class="fullWidth">
			<span class="imgCaption">E-Commerce Website, Shopping Cart</span>
		</a>
	</p>
	
	<p class="pageGalleryImg">
		<a href="../../images/shopPixelsScreen.jpg">
			<img src="../../images/shopPixelsScreen.jpg" class="fullWidth">
			<span class="imgCaption">CMS, Products Screen</span>
		</a>
	</p>
	
	<h2 class="clear">E-Hotel module</h2>
	
	<p>If you have a hotel or a guest house and you need a website with rooms reservation system, then this module is for you.</p>

	<ul>
		<li>Unlimited room types with prices</li>
		<li>Reservation pop-up with total price calculation upon number of nights and room's price</li>
		<li>Check-in and check-out drop-down calendar</li>
		<li>Back end new reservations notifications</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p class="pageGalleryImg" style="float: none; margin: 0 auto;">
		<a href="../../images/hotelHomeScreen.jpg">
