		</a>
	</p>
	
	<h2 class="clear">News module</h2>

	<p>This is an additional module to the basic website to be able to frequently add updates and news.</p>

	<ul>
		<li>Unlimited number of topics</li>
		<li>Unlimited number of articles</li>
